summary:
app 上架前的打包准备
1.检查是否是外网环境
2.更新info.plist文件版本号
3.product&mdash;&gt;scheme&mdash;-&gt;eidt scheme&mdash;&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp; build configuration 改为 release
4.build setting&mdash;&gt;architectures &ndash;&gt;&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp; build active architecture only 设置为NO
5.build setting&mdash;&gt; code signing &ndash;&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp; Provisioning&nbsp; Profile 设置发布证书
6. product clean
